title: LFT AP Support Main
body:
Support Main looking for team, I play every day at 6pm (afterwork) until 10pm. on friday nights and weekends potentially longer.
IGN: GangreneElbow
Age: 21
Role: Support
Located: Sydney, with constant 23Ping
Main Champ: Nidalee > Sona > Nami > Leona > Nautilus (Can play any AP support, and most tanks)

Preferably with an aggresive ADC player :D
